      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "To address behavior that undermines process without sounding accusatory, use terms like \"transparency\" and \"adherence to established communication channels.\" You might state, \"It is critical that all project decisions and information sharing occur through the documented channels to ensure comprehensive team awareness and alignment.\" This reframes the issue from dishonesty to a breakdown in established, necessary workflow. It focuses on the *system*, not their intent.",
